{"tid":42901,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【Now新聞台】與大公報記者爭執　梁天琦被捕","createTime":"2016-12-17T05:44:14.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-17T05:57:54.000Z","uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"93df43219886d6e843878da50329b0fbc3fe6925","tid":42901,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T05:44:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=204164\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D204164&d=L%2Bf6m%2BCTEttU5uIL0P8PbJkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=c279c81e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D204164&h=c0250377\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=204164</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】本土民主前線梁天琦被警方拘捕，涉及他八月時在港鐵站與《大公報》記者起爭執。<br />\n<br />\n梁天琦接受本台查詢時指警方星期五去到他位於太古的家中，以涉嫌在公眾地方打鬥，將他拘捕，並被帶往柴灣警署。<br />\n<br />\n律政司方面則未正式提出起訴。<br />\n<br />\n事發在八月中，梁天琦與《大公報》一名男記者在港鐵太古站發生爭執，事後梁天琦的上衣有損毀，而該名記者亦報警指被梁天琦襲擊。"},{"pid":"4d322d0bfa2660d64919c4b2b95affb340040c3e","tid":42901,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T05:48:45.000Z","msg":"個記者好似已經被起底？<br />\n<br />\n賤蟲一條"},{"pid":"b09dacb94356b302209a1f9eb99c2888bb86b387","tid":42901,"uid":23141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T05:54:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個記者好似已經被起底？<br />\n<br />\n賤蟲一條</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我記得起埋老婆仔女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67165256f9aa73d8bb0c19c9f1b369f9dde2324d","tid":42901,"uid":23141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T05:56:23.000Z","msg":"拉錯呀？「阿sir 做野唔使你教」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52d519e1edc0303ba01e44ed4cf294f2f1a0e77f","tid":42901,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T05:57:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}